The paper discusses the use of formal methods to enhance the safety assurance of Deep Neural Networks (DNNs), which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). However, since the focus is on safety assurance, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories, followed by cs.SY, cs.SE, and cs.CR.
